{"tid":981241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制派曾被否決開巴士線 　石籬去沙田無得揀　403小巴獨市","createTime":"2019-01-14T07:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T03:29:51.000Z","uid":20058,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"dd2c59484a30e1a1da587ba5a2aa150c2ce183d9","tid":981241,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:07:36.000Z","msg":"根據運輸署顯示，403號線小巴由進智公交旗下傑記運輸有限公司營辦，來往石籬（梨貝街）及沙田圍，途經梨木樹邨、城門隧道及沙田市中心。下線還有403A及403X，3線同樣經城門隧道，為葵青東及葵青北的居民來往新界東的唯一交通專線。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，由葵青區來往新界東區，除城門隧道之外，還有尖山隧道，但運輸署曾反對九巴開設巴士專線，令403號小巴專線繼續獨市經營。<br />\n<br />\n葵青區石籬北區議員林紹輝曾經去信運輸署，要求政府加開巴士線沿尖山隧道往新界東區，疏導城隧交通擠塞問題，他指：「今次意外根本就是運輸署做成的，你睇！東北葵有5個公屋，超過15萬居民，但整區只得3條專線小巴，每朝等小巴去新界東返工的市民都排晒長龍，小巴司機又唔夠人手，車又唔夠，咁咪要走多幾轉囉！」即使部份小巴改建為19座，也無助疏導人流。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">九巴在2018年6月曾經向運輸署申請47B專線由石籬往沙田市中心，但最終在區議會交通運輸委員會上被建制派否決。</span></span>林紹輝續說：「梗係啦！本來小巴就係獨市經營，你現在要開多條巴士線搶客，我係小巴公司都反對啦！」林促請運輸署加開尖山隧道巴士專線，改善東北葵居民來往新界東區的交通配套。<br />\n<br />\n另外，據葵青區石籬南區議員吳家超所指，葵青區往新界的小巴路線，大多會選擇城隧到，因為途經和宜合道，增加乘客量。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/282530/%E5%A5%AA%E5%91%BD%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D-%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA%E9%96%8B%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%B7%9A-%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E5%8E%BB%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E7%84%A1%E5%BE%97%E6%8F%80-403%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E7%8D%A8%E5%B8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F282530%2F%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25A6%258D-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E7%259F%25B3%25E7%25B1%25AC%25E5%258E%25BB%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25BE%2597%25E6%258F%2580-403%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25B8%2582&d=LAkC%2Fxj5WDMblhR9Z6BKdv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c57d7f37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/282530/%E5%A5%AA%E5%91%BD%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D-%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA%E9%96%8B%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%B7%9A-%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E5%8E%BB%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E7%84%A1%E5%BE%97%E6%8F%80-403%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E7%8D%A8%E5%B8%82</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41971e5550dc20a210f1a7c1b5fdda1f1cc0d56d","tid":981241,"uid":35430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"利益輸送佔9成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615baed358a5634ab063cbfa911612e2d948b75d","tid":981241,"uid":92859,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"建制派曾被否決❌<br />\n曾被建制派否決⭕️"},{"pid":"15e4d58cc919fd883fbf81e6074cf9445bab5115","tid":981241,"uid":106336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:38:37.000Z","msg":"又話尖山隧道隧道冇人用 依家九巴想開線做又ban<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f001cd45b7b05359eecbe91bf7840fd915bef184","tid":981241,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"個主題錯左"},{"pid":"5586fc484fae918e2a03aeb1d9a678e6474e8303","tid":981241,"uid":106336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/197107/%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E5%BE%80%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%8347b%E7%B7%9A%E5%91%8A%E5%90%B9-%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E6%96%A5%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%8A%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E6%BC%A0%E8%A6%96%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F197107%2F%25E7%259F%25B3%25E7%25B1%25AC%25E5%25BE%2580%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%25B8%2582